i havent written in this thing in almost a year. well on monday i start college once again while i work full time. im taking 3 classes. im watching drake and josh right now . i feeel like im gettin a little sick with a cough but nothing hardcore. i feel like everyone is flaking on me lately - that hasnt really changed. im still with anthony its gonna be 3.5 yrs in feb which is awesome. things are going great. my birthday is in less than a month. i want to find a good group of friends who arnt assholes or bitches like alot of my friends/old friends. well im out on my own right now im renting my room in some house in upland with some pretty cool people. im still working as a cashier and its pretty chill. i work monday through friday now with weekends off so its pretty cool. i just ffeeel like im wasting my weekends cuz i dont really do much and ive been sick on all the weekends ive had off - well its only be 2 weekends including this one hahah. but still. my sisters and i are doing pretty good. weve all been talking alot and im glad. wellllll im off now good night. imma try to write in this once a weeek ish.

well i just moved out of my house a couple weeks ago and im living with a family friend. im just tryin to get out there on my own and do my own things like get myself together. i think next week we (heather and i) are going to be movin out to an apartment or something like that imnot reallty sure. my life has become so busy lately. but i just cant wait to get all my stuff together and have a place of my own to call home i guess. i just couldnt take what was goin on at my house anymore. it was bull shit. but anyways i try to think of everything in a positive way. anthony and i are doing great 2 yrs and almost 7 months. so its going good. im in school and it sucks. i finally figured out wha ti wanna do with my life and i think i wanna do realestate or something like that for now. but i figure next yr ill be doing that. cuz the market is shit right now and i still have to take all my classes and what not. im watching blood diamond right now. its a good movie. everything is pretty ok right now. i been workin like crazy and going to school thats pretty much all i do. im kinda exhausted from it but i gotta do what i gotta do. things r somewhat good right now.

im so fucking frustrated. i dont know what to do with my self. im so bored all the time cuz everyone works or is at school. i just find my self playin halo all the time. im in college now im takin some bull shit classes but whatever, its somethin to do. i got a job but its gay i want a new one. i thought i would meet lots of new people in college, but thats not even the case. everyone is old as fukc and you can hardly even talk to them. i kinda miss my old friends. but i dont even talk to them anymore. next friday is my birthday, i wanna go to some show at the glass house but i might have to work then on sat i wanna go to a club but idk who would be down for that. i feel so alone sometimes. i dont like to admit that but i do. i catch my self like over reacting and shit and being all gay and emotional. idk why but i get that way sometimes.  i want to go back to church again. i have been praying alot lately, and god has been coming through for me. well i guess imma go to bed now, or just go lay down and think about shit i guess. i miss my dad so much.

i feel so lonely all the time. i cant wait for school to start so i can actually do stuff  makes new friends and what not. well december was like a really weird emotional month for me. it wasnt cuz of pms or anything. it was weird cuz it was during the whole month. like anything would piss me off or something. well this morning i registered for my classes got some good ones. whichis good. today is the biggest waste of day though. i cannt believe i did jack shit all day. today is just a sucky day. i put alot of trust into people and when they fuck that up idk its hard to get it back, cuz if they can lie to me the first time or do somethin the first time they obviously can do it a second time. no matter what it is.  when i trust someone i guess i am blinded that tey could ever do anythingn to hurt me. i gotta open my eyes up more and see whats actually going on with everything. just sucks when i have like 200% trust in someone and they fuck it up. then it just stays in the back of my mind. i just wanna be able to trust people. i wish i had a job i actually really do want but but it seems like whenever i try i just fail. im getting sick of that. puttin in the effort, for what? nothing. i think ive just been burned out lately.

well october 28th my grandma jan passed away. then october 29th my grandpa passed away(moms dad) . its like so crazy how things can happen when you least expect it. its really insane. right now well all this week i have intervies. i have like 5. and i gotta pick out my classes for college soon so i can go in january. yep. just seems like nothing is ever stable to me and that is one thing that i want most. is for things to be stable like they once were. christmas is commin in a few weeks. im not really excited like how i usually am. in all honestly what is there to look forward to? nothing much for me. it wont seem like christmas and i know its gonna be hard for us. but we seem to be getting through the hard times. in a way i finally feel like things are begining to look up for me - in a weird way. well only cuz im getin alot of call backs for jobs all randomly and shit. its crazy. i just want to be happy and have a stable life. i feel as if when things get a lil stable for me or somethin good happens, it onlybrings more b ad shit into my life. nothing can ever just be good. theres always bad that comes with it and im sick of it. today i got to thinkin that i want to live a healthy lifestyle andi want to job and play tennis again. its just very cold outside. so i wanted to get som elike cheap tred mill or something. idk just cuz i get so cold all the time. im done for now cuz i mpooped

well today is wack. krystle made me chocolate chip oatmeal cookies. we did like a bunch of yard work and cleaned up the back yard so it actually looks nice. we had shit all over the place cuz my ex step mother left her shit all over my back yard. but now it looks nice. ummm i didnt really do much today i just am watching a marathon of goosebumps. its pretty tight. i couldnt believe it was on. i feel like my friends suck right now besides like a few people. but everyone else fuck, people who i though ti was close to, people who i considered to be my best friends, they have drifted away. it sucks. im trying to get everything right. well like between my friends. i guess. im still looking for a job it sucks being broke when u have to pay rent. i spent my last like 400 $ on rent. it blows. ive never not had money before.  krystl eis a really good cook. she keeps makin really good food. she is like my mom in a way. she feeds me and makes sure im ok and stuff.  she is only like 3 yrs older than me though. welllll thats all for now. im really gonna try to keep writing in this so i can remember things.

i dont know what to write but i know i probably should. sometimes i feel like i cant go on anymore. but i keep pushing my self to because i need to be strong for my sisters. life is pretty hard for me right now. i have alot going on. when i think about my life i cant believe its mine. i cant believe how my life is. what ive been through and just how it is now. i try to be strong but it seems hard for me lately. everything is reminding me of my dad and just triggering old memories of him. when im around people and i get like a flash back of my dad i try not to cry because i dont want people to see me doing it. but its really hard for me not to cry . it happens everyday. something will pop into my head about my dad and it will just bring back memories or just like remind me of my dad. i miss him so much and i just cant believe he is not with us anymore. its just so unreal. when thanksgiving and christmas comes along it wont be the same. i dont give a care if i get any presents or anything for christmas cuz i just want my dad back. i dont know how things are going to be but it wont be the same. my grandma just told me yesterday that one of the things my dad wanted to see was me and my two sisters get married. that he wanted to get healthy so he could see us. that was very important to him. it breaks my heart that he wont be there physically. but i know he will be there with me in spirit. i want my dad to be there so bad when that day comes along. i wanted him to walk me down the aisle and everything. it just tears me apart inside :'[ . i want to be sucessful in life because i know that thats what my dad would have wanted. but i know my dad is with my mom again so that makes me feel alot better. my dad never lost his love for my mom. never. i just want them to be proud of me and the things i do. and that is what will drive me to be even more sucessful in life. i think about my parents every day, and im begining to pray everyday too, thats something i never really did. but it comforts me in a way. well thats all my writing for now.

it is crazy how your life can completly change in a short amount of time. a few weeks ago i received the news that my father and step mother would be getting a divorce within a month. hearing this news crushed me. the first thing that came to me would be my father's feelings and what was going to be happening real soon. my "step mother" kat would bemoving out on the first week of september. i honestly did not mind that. but then my fathehr told me that we would be selling the house by december 1st. ultimatly i was worried, i did not know where i would be living or anything, because i knew i was not going to move to the middle of no where arizona and leave certain people behind. that was not an option for me. due to the divorce situation i grew close with my dad, we talked about everyday for a good amount of time. he told me stuff that he didnt even tell my "step mother" .with the stress of finding a new place to live i had to do a bunch of college stuff, get a more high paying job, and get a new car. this was all very stressful to me, but then i got over it, and i accepted it.  then more bad news came, my finacial aid did not come through for college so basically i was finacially fucked because i can not afford college at this time in my life. but my father said he would pay, which i was reilived. last monday i took my placement test for college. i did pretty well on it. i came home and i talked to my dad about it. that monday i was going to go to the beach with my friend so my dad helped me pick out a good safe beach to go to. before i left to the beach my father checked all my oil in my car to make sure that i would be ok. tuesday was just a normal day to me , went to work, talked with my dad for a while, myspace, then hang with anthony. wednesday was the same. then thursday, friday, and saturday rolled around. i had not seen my dad. i didnt really think anything of it cuz it's normal for me to not see my dad cuz i am always in and out of the house working or just out. then sunday august 5th 2007 rolled around. i got up at appox. 11:20am , went on myspace for like a few mins, then i got a bang at my door. it was my stepmother. she yelled "call 911" . i opened my fuckin door and i saw my dad. i will never forget what i saw. i immediatly started to cry. because i already knew what i saw and what it meant. my father had passed away. that whole day seemed like a fuckin dream. i could not believe it at all. my last parent was no longer with me. i still cant believe it now. i dont really want to at this point. once i fully accept it, it wont be good. i try to be strong and not cry, but it is just so hard for me. i will hardlyy cry in front of people, only when i am alone. if you do ever see me cry that just means that i let my guard down. but i try to be strong not just for me, but for my 2 sisters aswell. because we are all in the same boat right now. parentless. my friends are now my family.

my senior year is almost done. i have about a week and a half left. im really excited to leave high school and not deal with the bull shit that comes along with it.

so therefore i will not be attending.
